screen_desc: The screenshot displays a messaging app interface for creating a new group. It shows a list of contacts that can be added, each with their name and last seen time. The group is titled "New Group" with a note indicating it can have up to 200,000 members. The contacts include various names, some with titles indicating their roles (e.g., "Back-end," "Manager"). The last seen times range from recently to specific times earlier in the day. There is also a navigation arrow at the bottom right for proceeding with the group creation.
